query.result:
40 He answered: “There is no certain place;  
41 It is lawful for me to go up and around;  
42 As far as I can go, I turn to you as guide.

43 But you already see how the day wanes,  
44 and to go up at night cannot be done;  
45 therefore it is good to think of a beautiful stay.

46 Souls are on the right here remote;  
47 if you permit me, I will bring you to them,  
